 it’s no joke. Also the pistachio one is sooooo good. Waiting for their grand opening specials 🥹🥹", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The extent of creaminess is insane and honestly it is not your regular yogurt smoothie. If you tried it you’ll know it’s no joke. Also the pistachio one is sooooo good. Waiting for their grand opening specials 🥹🥹", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Pingting Chen", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109938809552865577940/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIn064n48ZLHhbHhSMges20Oe9Uxz79o7miZLCgfl-IgxTLaQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-14T01:18:22.703890349Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pZMVdUQkpZbUpyWlRaeExXVlJjVlJ2UW5aMWIyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pZMVdUQkpZbUpyWlRaeExXVlJjVlJ2UW5aMWIyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80dcddca3a93dff5:0x1b09c18c286078e0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ9d-TOsrd3IAR4HhgKIzBCRs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kUlZuQmFiMGh4WTBRdGVHRkdRbU4xUkhKNllVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I can't describe how much i enjoyed their original avocaodo smoothie which is also their siganture drinks by the way.\n\nOriginal avocado yogurt smoothie: it's very creamy not just fruits blended with ice cubes. And i also love that the texture is very light bug satisfying at the same time.\n\nIf you are just gonna get one drink, then definitely their avocado series.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I can't describe how much i enjoyed their original avocaodo smoothie which is also their siganture drinks by the way.\n\nOriginal avocado yogurt smoothie: it's very creamy not just fruits blended with ice cubes. And i also love that the texture is very light bug satisfying at the same time.\n\nIf you are just gonna get one drink, then definitely their avocado series.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lulu Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111340358991650863471/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVH8tNgSgn_YVpwXRwEIMXAE8rHJ5kC3PEGBWj0WFfdKAFCzpKr=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-14T01:41:59.581430115Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kUlZuQmFiMGh4WTBRdGVHRkdRbU4xUkhKNllVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kUlZuQmFiMGh4WTBRdGVHRkdRbU4xUkhKNllVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80dcddca3a93dff5:0x1b09c18c286078e0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ9d-TOsrd3IAR4HhgKIzBCRs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pjNVdVWndkR2N3UzJaWlRrUjZRa050Vm0xQmMzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I loved this place in China and was so excited to hear they opened their first location in socal!! My favorite is definitely the original avocado smoothie. Their yogurt doesn’t have the tang signature to the yogurt in China, but the price probably explains why. The store is located conveniently straight across from the AMC and there’s a lot of cute outdoor seating areas for groups.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I loved this place in China and was so excited to hear they opened their first location in socal!! My favorite is definitely the original avocado smoothie. Their yogurt doesn’t have the tang signature to the yogurt in China, but the price probably explains why. The store is located conveniently straight across from the AMC and there’s a lot of cute outdoor seating areas for groups.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Emily H", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112084049898072792305/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXP-pHrBZ4nI-Lq653kiNDN4kW9HOCkF